summary: This is an email chain between FBI Special Agent Steve and another individual regarding the extraction of bookmarked items from case 50D-NY-3027571 for turnover to the SDNY (Southern District of New York). It shows coordination for evidence handling in an FBI investigation.

keyFacts: The FBI is handling case 50D-NY-3027571, which involves child exploitation/human trafficking.
Evidence from the case is being prepared for turnover to the Southern District of New York (SDNY).
The email shows internal FBI coordination for extracting specific bookmarked items from their case files.
